{
  "stem": "5891.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He'd walk up there with his little [INAUDIBLE] there, one after the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had all brushed our shoes, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyway, we did go to church.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then as-- for the school, you have to go to catechism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We did that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, when you're 13, 14, you got to confirmation, you're finished with your school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then you have to go into some household things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Just before I went-- we got arrested, I had just started my household year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was about 15 when I started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] he kept me for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He had a job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The war was already starting at that time, and he was working for the-- the city there, pulling wood with the wagon, cutting wood for the city.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so he kept us as long as he could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But that was a must.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You had to go for that year, that particular time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a requirement, yes, that you did go something for a year.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Household-- just the girls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, boys automatically went into like [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went into-- you know, girls didn't go in too much for the learning a trade at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was [GERMAN], housewife, and learning how to cook and how to clean, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's-- that's the situation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So house was very [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know my sister, in this one particular household-- was a big gas station they owned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a husband and wife, older folks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And were German people, and they had a-- run a gas station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Had a big 13-room home there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did a lot of entertaining.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my older sister Mathilde, who died in the camp, she worked there for a year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister Lena, she worked there for a year.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
